data.title: Emergency Dentist Stretford
data.meta_description: how it works - Dental Triage. 24 hour Emergency dentist in Manchester. Contact us today if you are in pain.
data.text:
Talk to Us

You can talk to the on-call dentist and request an appointment using the live chat feature or by calling us directly.

Book an Appointment

To confirm your appointment, there is a fee of Â£49 which can be paid online here.

Be seen

Once you have confirmed you appointment, you will then be seen by our dedicated friendly team who will go above and beyond to alleviate your dental pain.

Aftercare

Once your emergency treatment is complete, you can chose to be seen by us as a future patient. Alternatively, we can produce a report for your regular dentist for any follow up care required.
